message: "If you use this dataset or code, please cite the following."
title: "Tidal modulation of microplastic flux in a temperate estuary"
abstract: >-
  We quantify microplastic particle flux across a temperate tidal estuary over
  one lunar cycle and show a 2.3x enrichment on the ebb tide relative to slack
  water. Code and the sampling dataset are released for reproduction.
type: dataset
